04-05 June - Shrimp Scampi

- 1/3 cup oil
- 1   clove garlic
- 1   tablespoon parsley
- 2   tablespoon lemon juice
- 1/3 cup tomato paste
- 1/2 teaspoon salt
- 2   tablespoon chopped celery
- 1/2 tablespoon chopped green pepper
- 1   tablespoon chopped onion
- 1   lb shrimp
- 1/3 cup water

Heat oil, add shrimp, celery, green pepper, onion and garlic. Saute, turning often until shrimp are just pink. Turn heat to simmer. Add water and remaining ingredients and mix well. Simmer and stir occassionally about 5 minutes or until shrimp are tender. Can be served over rice or pasta. 